-- GM’s Opel Has No Current Plans to Close Plants, FAZ Reports
-- B y   A l e x   W e b b
-- 2012-02-08T16:52:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-08/gm-s-opel-has-no-current-plans-to-close-plants-faz-reports.html
General Motors Co. (GM) ’s Opel unit has no
current plans to shut plants, eliminate jobs or shift production
elsewhere,  Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung  reported in a preview
of an article to be published tomorrow, citing a letter from
Opel Chief Executive Officer Karl Friedrich Stracke to
employees.  Stracke told employees that measures still need to be taken
to reduce losses recorded in the previous year, FAZ said.
Stracke added that the measures would be made known after annual
results are officially released next week, the newspaper
reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
